[SPEAKER_00] i onda isto u usporedbi

521
00:26:17,180 --> 00:26:19,480
[SPEAKER_00] prema tome i u Hrvatskoj,

522
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:20,819
[SPEAKER_00] evo, i ovo što smo sad spominjali,

523
00:26:20,819 --> 00:26:23,700
[SPEAKER_00] da sam na podlju možda crkvene glazbe,

524
00:26:23,700 --> 00:26:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] ali isto tako, svi su ti skladitelji

525
00:26:25,880 --> 00:26:27,140
[SPEAKER_00] skladali svjetovnu glazbu.

526
00:26:27,140 --> 00:26:28,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne mogu sad recimo reći,

527
00:26:28,460 --> 00:26:30,480
[SPEAKER_00] ovoga, preskočiti Bernardina Sokola,

528
00:26:30,480 --> 00:26:33,119
[SPEAKER_00] koji je radio, to je ogroman opus,

529
00:26:33,119 --> 00:26:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] jel, on je bačen dole na Badi

530
00:26:34,539 --> 00:26:36,900
[SPEAKER_00] i Franjevac na 44.

531
00:26:37,259 --> 00:26:40,160
[SPEAKER_00] On je ubijenje, tako je, da.

532
00:26:40,160 --> 00:26:44,779
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to su više tisuća skladbi

533
00:26:44,779 --> 00:26:46,700
[SPEAKER_00] ili recimo dječjih ikroka

534
00:26:46,700 --> 00:26:49,299
[SPEAKER_00] za sve razdoblja godišnjih doba

535
00:26:49,299 --> 00:26:51,140
[SPEAKER_00] ili dječjeg uzrasta,

536
00:26:51,140 --> 00:26:54,299
[SPEAKER_00] čudesnih Ave Maria, Misa,

537
00:26:54,299 --> 00:26:56,660
[SPEAKER_00] mislim, to nema kraja tome

538
00:26:56,660 --> 00:26:58,220
[SPEAKER_00] koliko je taj opus, jel?

539
00:26:58,220 --> 00:27:00,420
[SPEAKER_00] I tako sve, recimo, onda sam radila

540
00:27:00,420 --> 00:27:01,859
[SPEAKER_00] velike projekte o Ivani Lango,

541
00:27:01,859 --> 00:27:03,900
[SPEAKER_00] Božidaru Kuncu, sad smo radili

542
00:27:03,900 --> 00:27:06,079
[SPEAKER_00] prije ovog zastoja

543
00:27:06,079 --> 00:27:07,660
[SPEAKER_00] Josipa Hacea.

544
00:27:07,660 --> 00:27:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, prošli mjesec sam radila sa studentima

545
00:27:09,960 --> 00:27:11,480
[SPEAKER_00] cijeli projekt Hrvatske oporete,

546
00:27:11,480 --> 00:27:13,440
[SPEAKER_00] sad su nazvali već u Split i tako,

547
00:27:13,440 --> 00:27:16,220
[SPEAKER_00] tako da, mislim, toga ima stvarno jako puno

548
00:27:16,220 --> 00:27:17,259
[SPEAKER_00] i to zaista volim.

549
00:27:17,259 --> 00:27:19,859
[SPEAKER_00] I onda, ako, mislim, ako vi nešto volite,

550
00:27:19,859 --> 00:27:21,400
[SPEAKER_00] onda to lakše prenesete

551
00:27:21,400 --> 00:27:23,299
[SPEAKER_00] tu ljubavi na te mlade ljude,

552
00:27:23,299 --> 00:27:25,680
[SPEAKER_00] tako da se oni u tom smislu nađu.

553
00:27:25,680 --> 00:27:27,299
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ispominjali ste da vaš kolegi,

554
00:27:27,299 --> 00:27:29,839
[SPEAKER_01] Hrvatska vokalna baština, koji vojite sa kolegicom

555
00:27:29,839 --> 00:27:32,460
[SPEAKER_01] Kristinom Bek Kukavčić, da on, u stvari,

556
00:27:32,460 --> 00:27:36,099
[SPEAKER_01] na neki način, je i platforma za ova sva moguća

557
00:27:36,099 --> 00:27:37,400
[SPEAKER_01] istraživanja koja radi.

558
00:27:37,640 --> 00:27:39,460
[SPEAKER_00] Asolutno, mislim da sam i kroz to

559
00:27:39,460 --> 00:27:41,619
[SPEAKER_00] sa Kristinom ovoga puno toga otkrila

560
00:27:41,619 --> 00:27:44,480
[SPEAKER_00] i možda će zvučat neskromno,

561
00:27:44,480 --> 00:27:46,500
[SPEAKER_00] ali mislim da je to jedan od najvrijednijih kolegija

562
00:27:46,500 --> 00:27:48,079
[SPEAKER_00] koji je u novije vrijeme

563
00:27:48,079 --> 00:27:51,119
[SPEAKER_00] uspostavljen i utemeljen na muzičkoj akademiji.

564
00:27:51,119 --> 00:27:52,440
[SPEAKER_00] On je izborni kolegi,

565
00:27:52,440 --> 00:27:54,700
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek ima velikog interes studenta

566
00:27:54,700 --> 00:27:56,940
[SPEAKER_00] i ovoga, mi smo, znači,

567
00:27:56,940 --> 00:27:59,819
[SPEAKER_00] sa studentima priredili preko stotinu

568
00:27:59,819 --> 00:28:02,619
[SPEAKER_00] skladbi hrvatskih skladatelja

569
00:28:02,619 --> 00:28:04,700
[SPEAKER_00] koji su vjerojatno prvi puta

570
00:28:04,700 --> 00:28:06,480
[SPEAKER_00] od svoje izvedbe izvedeni

571
00:28:06,480 --> 00:28:09,259
[SPEAKER_00] ili se vrlo rijetko izvode.

572
00:28:09,259 --> 00:28:11,420
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan postoji jedan ustaljen repertuar

573
00:28:11,420 --> 00:28:12,660
[SPEAKER_00] zadnjih desetljeća

574
00:28:12,660 --> 00:28:16,480
[SPEAKER_00] koji možda sadrži 10, 20, ajde 30 po pjevki.

575
00:28:16,480 --> 00:28:18,480
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, mi smo 150 izveli

576
00:28:18,480 --> 00:28:20,460
[SPEAKER_00] koje nisu uopće na repertuaru.

577
00:28:20,460 --> 00:28:21,660
[SPEAKER_00] I sada ti mladi ljudi

578
00:28:21,660 --> 00:28:23,319
[SPEAKER_00] koji opet rade u glazbonim školama,

579
00:28:23,319 --> 00:28:25,400
[SPEAKER_00] oni mogu to opet dalje,

580
00:28:25,400 --> 00:28:26,319
[SPEAKER_00] to živi.

581
00:28:26,319 --> 00:28:29,220
[SPEAKER_00] Ili to sad je na koncertnim pozornicama.

582
00:28:29,220 --> 00:28:31,559
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nekako smo to oživjeli.

583
00:28:31,559 --> 00:28:34,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo, kolegi već sad traje više od 10 godina,

584
00:28:34,099 --> 00:28:36,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali moralo je proći to.

585
00:28:36,480 --> 00:28:38,500
[SPEAKER_01] pa da, pa naravno, moralo je proći.

586
00:28:38,500 --> 00:28:42,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, pa da, to je opet vezano za identitet.

587
00:28:42,420 --> 00:28:45,480
[SPEAKER_01] Sve se vraća tome da kako ti možeš biti,

588
00:28:45,480 --> 00:28:48,740
[SPEAKER_01] imat jasan odnos prema tome

589
00:28:48,740 --> 00:28:50,500
[SPEAKER_01] tko si ti, kakav je tvoj narod,

590
00:28:50,500 --> 00:28:52,559
[SPEAKER_01] ako uopće ne poznaješ svoju kulturu.

591
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:55,339
[SPEAKER_00] Naši studenti odu recimo negdje van na seminare,

592
00:28:55,339 --> 00:28:56,720
[SPEAKER_00] na natjecanja i onda ih pitaju

593
00:28:56,720 --> 00:28:58,579
[SPEAKER_00] dajte nam neku vašu iz Hrvatske.

594
00:28:58,579 --> 00:29:00,240
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda je to vrlo skromno,

595
00:29:00,240 --> 00:29:01,619
[SPEAKER_00] ne, onda zovu uvijek Kristinu,

596
00:29:01,619 --> 00:29:02,720
[SPEAKER_00] joj, dajte nam nešto.

597
00:29:02,720 --> 00:29:05,500
[SPEAKER_00] I onda pokažu i tamo i onda su svi zadivljeni.

598
00:29:05,740 --> 00:29:08,519
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, sad je, recimo, strašno popularna

599
00:29:08,519 --> 00:29:09,680
[SPEAKER_00] postala Dora Pejačević.

600
00:29:09,680 --> 00:29:12,299
[SPEAKER_00] Nema, gdje ju se ne izvodi, gdje ju se snima.

601
00:29:12,299 --> 00:29:14,839
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan student je isto prijedno deseta godina

602
00:29:14,839 --> 00:29:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] kod nas bio na razmini iz Amerike,

603
00:29:16,500 --> 00:29:19,160
[SPEAKER_00] iz Indijana je bio kod mene isto na ovom kolegiju

604
00:29:19,160 --> 00:29:21,259
[SPEAKER_00] i on je svoj diplomski u Americi radio

605
00:29:21,259 --> 00:29:22,240
[SPEAKER_00] o Dori Pejačević.

606
00:29:22,240 --> 00:29:24,259
[SPEAKER_00] I našao je po svjetskim knjižicama

607
00:29:24,259 --> 00:29:26,920
[SPEAKER_00] ono što mi još ovdje nismo tada bili znali, recimo.

608
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:27,599
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da.

609
00:29:27,599 --> 00:29:28,539
[SPEAKER_00] To je fascinantno.

610
00:29:28,539 --> 00:29:31,559
[SPEAKER_00] Amerikanac ima priču o Dori Pejačević, jel?

611
00:29:31,559 --> 00:29:34,839
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, evo, ni sami nismo svjesni

612
00:29:34,839 --> 00:29:38,599
[SPEAKER_00] koliko ponosni možemo biti na ono što imamo.

613
00:29:38,599 --> 00:29:39,299
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, tako.

614
00:29:39,299 --> 00:29:42,880
[SPEAKER_01] Vi ste i ovoj povezano s tim često naglašavate

615
00:29:42,880 --> 00:29:46,019
[SPEAKER_01] kako vam je veliko zadovoljstvo rad sa studentima.

616
00:29:46,019 --> 00:29:49,099
[SPEAKER_01] Imate i svoje studente doma,

617
00:29:49,099 --> 00:29:53,299
[SPEAKER_01] imate ove koji su vaša duhovna djeca, jel,

618
00:29:53,299 --> 00:29:56,779
[SPEAKER_01] na neki način, koje podučavate sve što znate,

619
00:29:56,920 --> 00:30:00,500
[SPEAKER_01] ali baš me, negdje sam jedan vaš intervju čitala

620
00:30:00,500 --> 00:30:05,400
[SPEAKER_01] i baš mi je bilo, probijalo je to oduševljenje

621
00:30:05,400 --> 00:30:07,920
[SPEAKER_01] s tim mladim ljudima i to je tako lijepo vidjeti

622
00:30:07,920 --> 00:30:09,799
[SPEAKER_01] da često ljudi pričaju negativno,

623
00:30:09,799 --> 00:30:11,400
[SPEAKER_01] pa mladi su ovako, mladi su onakvi,

624
00:30:11,400 --> 00:30:13,059
[SPEAKER_01] ali na kraju ima ih toliko prekrasnih

625
00:30:13,059 --> 00:30:14,880
[SPEAKER_01] da mi je bilo divno čuti ovo.

626
00:30:14,880 --> 00:30:17,059
[SPEAKER_00] Je, ja ne kažem da se ponovo rodim ono što se kaže

627
00:30:17,059 --> 00:30:18,759
[SPEAKER_00] bi radila isti posao ovoga.

628
00:30:18,759 --> 00:30:22,359
[SPEAKER_00] Vi dobijete tog mladog čovjeka od 18-20 godina pred sebe.

629
00:30:22,900 --> 00:30:25,079
[SPEAKER_00] Moram priznati da, evo, koliko radim,

630
00:30:25,079 --> 00:30:28,759
[SPEAKER_00] se ta, gledam ta lica kad dolaze na te prijemne ispite,

631
00:30:28,759 --> 00:30:32,259
[SPEAKER_00] ipak se mijenjaju, nisu to, nekad, znate,

632
00:30:32,259 --> 00:30:34,180
[SPEAKER_00] možda vidim previše ovih ekrana,

633
00:30:34,180 --> 00:30:36,559
[SPEAKER_00] pa da više gledaju kroz mene nego u mene,

634
00:30:36,559 --> 00:30:39,119
[SPEAKER_00] pa da je možda mimika i gestikulacija lica

635
00:30:39,119 --> 00:30:40,180
[SPEAKER_00] postala manja.

636
00:30:40,180 --> 00:30:43,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ali evo, dobila sam ih, kako bi se reklo,

637
00:30:43,279 --> 00:30:45,420
[SPEAKER_00] na dlanu priliku da u tih pet godina

638
00:30:45,420 --> 00:30:48,019
[SPEAKER_00] njihovoga studija možda će biti više sa mnom

639
00:30:48,019 --> 00:30:49,859
[SPEAKER_00] nego sa svojom obitelji i roditeljima.

640
00:30:49,859 --> 00:30:52,220
[SPEAKER_00] I dobila sam i od njihovih roditelja

641
00:30:52,220 --> 00:30:54,119
[SPEAKER_00] na povjerenje njih,

642
00:30:54,119 --> 00:30:56,140
[SPEAKER_00] da nešto od njih stvorim

643
00:30:56,140 --> 00:30:58,680
[SPEAKER_00] i na koncu uvijek mi je prekrasno vidjeti

644
00:30:58,680 --> 00:31:01,019
[SPEAKER_00] njihova onako plaha i plašljiva lica

645
00:31:01,019 --> 00:31:02,980
[SPEAKER_00] na prvoj godini i onda kad ih vidim

646
00:31:02,980 --> 00:31:04,220
[SPEAKER_00] zrele na pozornici,

647
00:31:04,220 --> 00:31:06,579
[SPEAKER_00] znate, nema veće sreće kad ih vidite

648
00:31:06,579 --> 00:31:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] ko ozbiljne umjetnike i to.

649
00:31:08,039 --> 00:31:11,059
[SPEAKER_00] I to onda ostaju i trajna i dugotrajna

650
00:31:11,059 --> 00:31:12,859
[SPEAKER_00] i prijateljstva i poznanstva

651
00:31:13,380 --> 00:31:15,799
[SPEAKER_00] i čak i kumstva, da ne kažem,

652
00:31:15,799 --> 00:31:19,259
[SPEAKER_00] povezanost jedna i na koncertnim pozornicama

653
00:31:19,259 --> 00:31:20,559
[SPEAKER_00] i kasnije na snimanjima.

654
00:31:20,559 --> 00:31:23,920
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da evo, to je stvarno nešto posebno.

655
00:31:23,920 --> 00:31:25,740
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam, jel drugi nastavnici,

656
00:31:25,740 --> 00:31:29,960
[SPEAKER_00] ako su učilišni u tim 200-300 studenta,

657
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:30,740
[SPEAKER_00] to opće se ne mogu zamisli.

658
00:31:30,740 --> 00:31:31,980
[SPEAKER_00] Zamisli tako nešto.

659
00:31:31,980 --> 00:31:33,900
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, vi imate priliku raditi individualno.

660
00:31:33,900 --> 00:31:35,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ja, individualno i tako da se mi

661
00:31:35,579 --> 00:31:37,700
[SPEAKER_00] jako povezujemo, jel?

662
00:31:37,700 --> 00:31:39,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ne može to biti samo odnost

663
00:31:39,259 --> 00:31:41,440
[SPEAKER_00] profesor-student, jer ako je,

664
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:43,740
[SPEAKER_00] onda to umjetnosti ne funkcionira,

665
00:31:43,740 --> 00:31:45,019
[SPEAKER_00] ali ako se mi bolje kužimo,

666
00:31:45,019 --> 00:31:46,480
[SPEAKER_00] ta naša umjetnost je kvalitetnija.

667
00:31:46,480 --> 00:31:47,859
[SPEAKER_00] Bolje, kvalitetnija, tako je.

668
00:31:47,859 --> 00:31:49,759
[SPEAKER_01] Vi imate četvero djece.

669
00:31:49,759 --> 00:31:49,980
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

670
00:31:49,980 --> 00:31:50,660
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro.

671
00:31:50,660 --> 00:31:53,339
[SPEAKER_01] I dvoje su isto tako glazbenici, jel tako?

672
00:31:53,339 --> 00:31:55,500
[SPEAKER_00] Hrana je diplomirao čembalo

673
00:31:55,500 --> 00:31:56,880
[SPEAKER_00] i dirigiranje,

674
00:31:56,880 --> 00:31:59,480
[SPEAKER_00] a Josipa je diplomirala pjevanje

675
00:31:59,480 --> 00:32:00,980
[SPEAKER_00] i oboje su uspješni.

676
00:32:00,980 --> 00:32:02,380
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, Franja je bio proglašen,

677
00:32:02,380 --> 00:32:03,619
[SPEAKER_00] znači, i prije dvije godine

678
00:32:03,619 --> 00:32:05,519
[SPEAKER_00] i najboljim hrvatskim mladim glazbenikom.

679
00:32:05,519 --> 00:32:07,500
[SPEAKER_00] Bio je tri godine čak na Erasmusu,

680
00:32:07,500 --> 00:32:08,539
[SPEAKER_00] diljem Evrope.

681
00:32:08,539 --> 00:32:11,460
[SPEAKER_00] Josipa, evo, svaja isto vrhunske nagrade,

682
00:32:11,460 --> 00:32:13,839
[SPEAKER_00] već pjeva posvuda i tako.

683
00:32:13,839 --> 00:32:16,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ali vi ste, vi ste isto iz obitelji glazbenika,

684
00:32:16,440 --> 00:32:18,279
[SPEAKER_01] vaš muž je također.

685
00:32:18,279 --> 00:32:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, dajte nam malo riječi

686
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:22,460
[SPEAKER_01] kako to funkcionira u tim glazbeničkim obiteljima.

687
00:32:22,460 --> 00:32:23,579
[SPEAKER_01] Pa meni je to normalno.

688
00:32:23,579 --> 00:32:27,339
[SPEAKER_01] Znam, znam, ali evo namo drugima ispričate malo da.

689
00:32:27,359 --> 00:32:29,259
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ta glazba je, znate što ja mislim,

690
00:32:29,259 --> 00:32:31,140
[SPEAKER_00] ja mislim da je to tako nekad i bilo,

691
00:32:31,140 --> 00:32:32,559
[SPEAKER_00] sve građanske obitelji su imali

692
00:32:32,559 --> 00:32:35,420
[SPEAKER_00] jako visoku razinu glazbenog obrazovanja.

693
00:32:35,420 --> 00:32:37,160
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, ovo što čitam, recimo obitelj Bersa,

694
00:32:37,160 --> 00:32:38,980
[SPEAKER_00] Vladoje, Blagoje, ne znam,

695
00:32:38,980 --> 00:32:41,640
[SPEAKER_00] Vladimir Bersa, kunc obitelj,

696
00:32:41,640 --> 00:32:44,019
[SPEAKER_00] oni su svi, bili su odvjetnici, lječnici,

697
00:32:44,019 --> 00:32:46,279
[SPEAKER_00] recimo Rudolf Maci u temelju

698
00:32:46,279 --> 00:32:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] glazbenog društva intelektualaca,

699
00:32:47,880 --> 00:32:49,920
[SPEAKER_00] ansamble, kvartete,

700
00:32:50,000 --> 00:32:51,240
[SPEAKER_00] to su sve bili amateri,

701
00:32:51,240 --> 00:32:52,660
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, to su sve bili ljudi

702
00:32:52,660 --> 00:32:54,759
[SPEAKER_00] koji su se bavili sasvim nečim drugim,

703
00:32:54,759 --> 00:32:57,140
[SPEAKER_00] ali se, svi su znali svira.

704
00:32:57,140 --> 00:32:58,619
[SPEAKER_00] Cijeli Zagreb je zapravo svirao,

705
00:32:58,619 --> 00:33:00,059
[SPEAKER_00] a Zagreb je bio do glavnog kolodvora,

706
00:33:00,059 --> 00:33:01,539
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, nije to i do kvatriča,

707
00:33:01,539 --> 00:33:03,680
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, ne možemo uzeti ovo što danas ima.

708
00:33:03,680 --> 00:33:04,859
[SPEAKER_00] Ali svi su bili,

709
00:33:04,859 --> 00:33:05,839
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam,

710
00:33:05,839 --> 00:33:08,619
[SPEAKER_00] sad u arhivu istražujući sve,

711
00:33:08,619 --> 00:33:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] sam to vidjela da su svi nešto svirali,

712
00:33:10,599 --> 00:33:12,359
[SPEAKER_00] nema, i tih jako poznatih imena,

713
00:33:12,359 --> 00:33:14,460
[SPEAKER_00] vidite ih da su bili članovi zborova.

714
00:33:14,460 --> 00:33:16,279
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da je to u moje obitelji

715
00:33:16,279 --> 00:33:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] nekako očito ostalo.

716
00:33:17,559 --> 00:33:18,720
[SPEAKER_00] Moja nona, ja znam,

717
00:33:18,720 --> 00:33:19,740
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam ju se sjećan

718
00:33:19,740 --> 00:33:21,720
[SPEAKER_00] kako je prekrasno pjevala ona iz Primorja,

719
00:33:21,720 --> 00:33:24,640
[SPEAKER_00] u praputnjaka iznad Bakarskog zaljeva.

720
00:33:24,640 --> 00:33:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] Mama je bila učiteljica,

721
00:33:26,599 --> 00:33:27,660
[SPEAKER_00] znači harmonike,

722
00:33:27,660 --> 00:33:29,759
[SPEAKER_00] ona isto završila akademiju.

723
00:33:29,759 --> 00:33:31,559
[SPEAKER_00] Tata je strašno volio glazbu,

724
00:33:31,640 --> 00:33:33,720
[SPEAKER_00] on je završio dvije godine srednju glazbenu školu,

725
00:33:33,720 --> 00:33:35,619
[SPEAKER_00] svirao je jazz i popularnu glazbu

726
00:33:35,619 --> 00:33:38,619
[SPEAKER_00] i kad smo sestra i ja krenule u glazbenu školu,

727
00:33:38,619 --> 00:33:42,259
[SPEAKER_00] on je često plakao koliko je bio žalostan

728
00:33:42,259 --> 00:33:44,960
[SPEAKER_00] što se on nije životno opredijelio tome,

729
00:33:44,960 --> 00:33:46,460
[SPEAKER_00] nego je bio inženjer kemije.

730
00:33:46,460 --> 00:33:49,460
[SPEAKER_00] Tete su, isto tako, sve su.

731
00:33:49,460 --> 00:33:50,660
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, moja nona,

732
00:33:50,660 --> 00:33:52,980
[SPEAKER_00] koja je bila zapravo priprosta,

733
00:33:52,980 --> 00:33:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] jednostavna žena,

734
00:33:54,000 --> 00:33:56,660
[SPEAKER_00] je svi svoj četverok čeri poslala

735
00:33:56,660 --> 00:33:58,319
[SPEAKER_00] i svi su išli u glazbenu školu.

736
00:33:58,319 --> 00:34:00,359
[SPEAKER_00] Nisu sve profesionalne glazbenice,

737
00:34:00,460 --> 00:34:01,900
[SPEAKER_00] ali isto tako imaju...

738
00:34:01,900 --> 00:34:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno su poznali glazben.

739
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:04,940
[SPEAKER_00] Moj djed, po tatinoj strani,

740
00:34:04,940 --> 00:34:05,660
[SPEAKER_00] iz Virovitice,

741
00:34:05,660 --> 00:34:07,299
[SPEAKER_00] on je svirao taj rijetki instrument

742
00:34:07,299 --> 00:34:08,699
[SPEAKER_00] pjevajuću pilu.

743
00:34:08,699 --> 00:34:10,880
[SPEAKER_00] To se i danas malo glazbenika zna,

744
00:34:10,880 --> 00:34:13,099
[SPEAKER_00] to su zapravo limeni vojni orkestre imali,

745
00:34:13,099 --> 00:34:13,820
[SPEAKER_00] jedna pila,

746
00:34:13,820 --> 00:34:14,960
[SPEAKER_00] zaista je zlako pila,

747
00:34:14,960 --> 00:34:15,860
[SPEAKER_00] koja se jako savijala

748
00:34:15,860 --> 00:34:17,400
[SPEAKER_00] i sa gudalom se po njoj svirala

749
00:34:17,400 --> 00:34:18,920
[SPEAKER_00] i onda kako ste ju savili,

750
00:34:18,920 --> 00:34:20,940
[SPEAKER_00] tako ste dobijali različitu visinu tonova.

751
00:34:20,940 --> 00:34:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] To je bilo isto posebno u Mijeće

752
00:34:22,420 --> 00:34:24,800
[SPEAKER_00] i to se Dide Sjećan kako je to svirao

753
00:34:24,800 --> 00:34:26,380
[SPEAKER_00] i violinu je Dide svirao.

754
00:34:26,380 --> 00:34:28,820
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da je to nekako bilo sasvim normalno.

755
00:34:28,820 --> 00:34:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, suprug,

756
00:34:29,380 --> 00:34:30,679
[SPEAKER_00] ja smo od akademije,

757
00:34:30,679 --> 00:34:31,900
[SPEAKER_00] od prve godine zajedno

758
00:34:31,900 --> 00:34:33,659
[SPEAKER_00] i tako da je onda i naša djeca,

759
00:34:33,659 --> 00:34:34,679
[SPEAKER_00] ja kad čim sam rodila,

760
00:34:34,679 --> 00:34:36,619
[SPEAKER_00] još u Trbugu su svudi išli sa mnom.

761
00:34:37,280 --> 00:34:40,119
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da je to sve nekako normalno da se svira.

762
00:34:40,119 --> 00:34:43,019
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, i što bi vi sada savitovali roditeljima

763
00:34:43,019 --> 00:34:44,800
[SPEAKER_01] koji nisu ovako glazbenički obidini?

764
00:34:44,800 --> 00:34:46,360
[SPEAKER_01] Naprimjer, da roditelji sami nemaju

765
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:47,900
[SPEAKER_01] obrazovanje glazbeno

766
00:34:47,900 --> 00:34:49,380
[SPEAKER_01] u odnosu na njihovu djecu.

767
00:34:49,380 --> 00:34:53,119
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, vezano za proširivanje te glazbene kulture.

768
00:34:53,119 --> 00:34:54,940
[SPEAKER_00] To je malo više slojno.

769
00:34:54,940 --> 00:34:58,599
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, ja sam sudator učbenika za glazbenu kulturu,

770
00:34:58,599 --> 00:35:01,679
[SPEAKER_00] pa vidim kako je to danas zapravo jako skromno

771
00:35:01,679 --> 00:35:03,320
[SPEAKER_00] i kako se ne očekuje puno

772
00:35:03,320 --> 00:35:06,420
[SPEAKER_00] i kako je relativno i to malo sati,

773
00:35:06,420 --> 00:35:10,059
[SPEAKER_00] a onda i cijelo ozračje društveno

774
00:35:10,059 --> 00:35:13,860
[SPEAKER_00] nije u tom smislu da stimulira i oblikuje,

775
00:35:13,860 --> 00:35:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] nemam ništa protiv popularne ove glazbe,

776
00:35:16,500 --> 00:35:17,780
[SPEAKER_00] jel to je sve u redu,

777
00:35:17,780 --> 00:35:20,519
[SPEAKER_00] ali da se i više stimulira i ovu djecu

778
00:35:20,519 --> 00:35:22,480
[SPEAKER_00] koja svira u obitelji, koje svira i tako.

779
00:35:22,480 --> 00:35:23,900
[SPEAKER_00] I nas trenutno ima jako puno

780
00:35:23,900 --> 00:35:25,440
[SPEAKER_00] u hrvatskoj obitelji glazbenika.

781
00:35:25,440 --> 00:35:26,900
[SPEAKER_00] Baš se ima jako puno.

782
00:35:26,900 --> 00:35:29,699
[SPEAKER_00] Čak su već ovo djeca nam i završila studije.

783
00:35:29,699 --> 00:35:34,480
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da je teško reći

784
00:35:34,480 --> 00:35:36,480
[SPEAKER_00] ako roditelj ne zna,

785
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:39,559
[SPEAKER_00] teško mu je sigurno prepoznati to u svom djetetu.

786
00:35:39,559 --> 00:35:40,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam to mogla prepoznati,

787
00:35:40,840 --> 00:35:41,800
[SPEAKER_00] mogla sam njegovati,

788
00:35:41,800 --> 00:35:44,400
[SPEAKER_00] mogla sam djetetu ponuditi najbolju učitelja

789
00:35:44,400 --> 00:35:45,980
[SPEAKER_00] ili školu jer sam to znala.

790
00:35:46,400 --> 00:35:49,800
[SPEAKER_00] A s druge strane, evo ja vodim dječi zbor u svojoj župi.

791
00:35:49,800 --> 00:35:51,900
[SPEAKER_00] To je u Lučkom.

792
00:35:51,900 --> 00:35:53,800
[SPEAKER_00] Lučko se i tog Ivana ne pomuka.

793
00:35:53,800 --> 00:35:58,400
[SPEAKER_00] I evo naš prekrasan župnik Dubroko Škrlin Hren koji me pozvao.

794
00:35:58,400 --> 00:36:02,019
[SPEAKER_00] Isto sam rekla pa kuću ne mogu više od svega toga.

795
00:36:02,019 --> 00:36:04,119
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, ja mislim da je to zadnje što bi odustala

796
00:36:04,119 --> 00:36:05,820
[SPEAKER_00] tu taj dječi zbor koji vodim.

797
00:36:05,960 --> 00:36:07,860
[SPEAKER_00] To mi je nešto melem za dušu.

798
00:36:07,860 --> 00:36:09,039
[SPEAKER_00] To je nešto prekrasno.

799
00:36:09,039 --> 00:36:12,500
[SPEAKER_00] I isto vidim koliko ima darovite djece

800
00:36:12,500 --> 00:36:16,820
[SPEAKER_00] i potičem roditelje isto tako da upisuju djecu u glazbenu školu.

801
00:36:16,820 --> 00:36:19,099
[SPEAKER_00] I sad ih imamo jedno šest, sedam od njih dvadeset

802
00:36:19,099 --> 00:36:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] koji su krenuli u glazbenu školu.

803
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:23,519
[SPEAKER_00] Još se troje sad, evo budem im pomogla

804
00:36:23,519 --> 00:36:25,760
[SPEAKER_00] da se pripreme za prijemne ispite.

805
00:36:25,760 --> 00:36:27,579
[SPEAKER_00] I mi smo relativno daleko od Zagreba

806
00:36:27,579 --> 00:36:29,139
[SPEAKER_00] i nemamo blizu glazbenu školu.

807
00:36:29,139 --> 00:36:30,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ja znam da je to velika žrtva.

808
00:36:30,820 --> 00:36:32,519
[SPEAKER_00] To je zaista velika žrtva.

809
00:36:32,519 --> 00:36:34,980
[SPEAKER_00] Evo ja iz svog primjera tvrdim

810
00:36:34,980 --> 00:36:37,280
[SPEAKER_00] da sam jedno najmanje 3-4 godine

811
00:36:37,280 --> 00:36:38,900
[SPEAKER_00] možda i više nisam to bilježila.

812
00:36:38,900 --> 00:36:40,719
[SPEAKER_00] Čak mi je sad nekad žao kad se sjetim

813
00:36:40,719 --> 00:36:42,719
[SPEAKER_00] kako smo pisali u kući te rasporede

814
00:36:42,719 --> 00:36:44,239
[SPEAKER_00] kad, ko, koga, vozi gdje smo.

815
00:36:44,239 --> 00:36:47,500
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki dan od 6 do 10 smo mi bili u autu.

816
00:36:47,500 --> 00:36:48,519
[SPEAKER_00] Pa bi mi djeca...

817
00:36:48,519 --> 00:36:50,320
[SPEAKER_00] Mama krivo si skrenula, ja sad imam muzičku.

818
00:36:50,320 --> 00:36:52,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ti ideš na sport ili su i sportove trenirali.

819
00:36:52,739 --> 00:36:54,820
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da...

820
00:36:54,820 --> 00:36:56,840
[SPEAKER_00] Evo sad ubiramo plodove.

821
00:36:56,840 --> 00:36:58,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ja uvijek kažem

822
00:36:58,920 --> 00:37:01,119
[SPEAKER_01] ovim sad mladim obiteljima

823
00:37:01,119 --> 00:37:02,980
[SPEAKER_01] koje imaju više djece

824
00:37:02,980 --> 00:37:04,320
[SPEAKER_01] i naporan...

825
00:37:04,320 --> 00:37:05,619
[SPEAKER_01] sad su u ovom dijelu života.

826
00:37:05,619 --> 00:37:06,079
[SPEAKER_01] I uvijek kažem

827
00:37:06,079 --> 00:37:07,019
[SPEAKER_01] to će proć

828
00:37:07,019 --> 00:37:08,300
[SPEAKER_01] a onda će te uživati.

829
00:37:08,300 --> 00:37:09,300
[SPEAKER_01] Da, je li to isto?

830
00:37:09,300 --> 00:37:09,840
[SPEAKER_01] Istina, istina.

831
00:37:09,840 --> 00:37:10,920
[SPEAKER_01] To isto isplati se uložiti.

832
00:37:10,920 --> 00:37:12,239
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ima jedan dio

833
00:37:12,239 --> 00:37:15,179
[SPEAKER_01] to znadem čuti od prijateljica

834
00:37:15,179 --> 00:37:16,159
[SPEAKER_01] ili u obitelji

835
00:37:16,159 --> 00:37:17,880
[SPEAKER_01] da jedan dio problema

836
00:37:17,880 --> 00:37:19,539
[SPEAKER_01] jest u nekim glazbenim školama

837
00:37:19,539 --> 00:37:20,900
[SPEAKER_01] što se u principu očekuje

838
00:37:20,900 --> 00:37:22,400
[SPEAKER_01] da djeca budu...

839
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:23,719
[SPEAKER_01] Da ih oni obrezuju

840
00:37:23,719 --> 00:37:25,260
[SPEAKER_01] da oni budu glazbenici.

841
00:37:25,260 --> 00:37:27,639
[SPEAKER_01] a u stvari je cijelj jednog dijela rojtelja

842
00:37:27,639 --> 00:37:29,320
[SPEAKER_01] da djeca prošire svoju kulturu.

843
00:37:29,320 --> 00:37:30,519
[SPEAKER_01] Da upravo ono

844
00:37:30,519 --> 00:37:32,099
[SPEAKER_01] o čemu ste pričali u Zagrebu.

845
00:37:32,099 --> 00:37:33,340
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto on ne bi znao

846
00:37:33,340 --> 00:37:34,880
[SPEAKER_01] svirati neki instrument

847
00:37:34,880 --> 00:37:36,480
[SPEAKER_01] bez da mu to bude profesit,

848
00:37:36,480 --> 00:37:37,519
[SPEAKER_01] da mu to bude karijera?

849
00:37:37,960 --> 00:37:38,340
[SPEAKER_00] Točno.

850
00:37:38,340 --> 00:37:40,420
[SPEAKER_00] Jel sad su škole naše

851
00:37:40,420 --> 00:37:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] zaista imaju svoj školski program,

852
00:37:42,500 --> 00:37:43,199
[SPEAKER_00] državne su,

853
00:37:43,199 --> 00:37:44,519
[SPEAKER_00] jel imamo nešto privatnih

854
00:37:44,519 --> 00:37:45,599
[SPEAKER_00] i tada u to vrijeme

855
00:37:45,599 --> 00:37:46,440
[SPEAKER_00] o kojem sam pričala

856
00:37:46,440 --> 00:37:48,300
[SPEAKER_00] je bilo i bio je konzervatorije

857
00:37:48,300 --> 00:37:49,619
[SPEAKER_00] tada glazbeni zavod,

858
00:37:49,619 --> 00:37:51,239
[SPEAKER_00] ali je bilo nekoliko privatnih škola

859
00:37:51,239 --> 00:37:53,780
[SPEAKER_00] i mislim recimo što u Njemačkoj

860
00:37:53,780 --> 00:37:54,619
[SPEAKER_00] i vani postojte,

861
00:37:54,619 --> 00:37:56,500
[SPEAKER_00] nema tog prijemnog ispita.

862
00:37:56,500 --> 00:37:57,579
[SPEAKER_00] Sva djeca upisuju.

863
00:37:57,579 --> 00:37:58,880
[SPEAKER_00] Jel pa se to s vremenom

864
00:37:58,880 --> 00:37:59,559
[SPEAKER_00] i ja isto tvrdim

865
00:37:59,559 --> 00:38:00,400
[SPEAKER_00] razvije se,

866
00:38:00,400 --> 00:38:01,719
[SPEAKER_00] razvije se ako se na vrijeme

867
00:38:01,719 --> 00:38:03,659
[SPEAKER_00] krene ono za nekog etiketa

868
00:38:03,659 --> 00:38:04,519
[SPEAKER_00] da nemaš sluha

869
00:38:04,519 --> 00:38:06,159
[SPEAKER_00] je jako gruba

870
00:38:06,159 --> 00:38:07,380
[SPEAKER_00] i čovjeku to ostane

871
00:38:07,380 --> 00:38:08,679
[SPEAKER_00] i ono ostane uvjeren

872
00:38:08,679 --> 00:38:09,619
[SPEAKER_00] da nema sluha.

873
00:38:09,619 --> 00:38:12,139
[SPEAKER_00] A to se zaista može izvježbat.

874
00:38:12,139 --> 00:38:12,820
[SPEAKER_00] To nije točno.

875
00:38:12,820 --> 00:38:13,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam dobila

876
00:38:13,400 --> 00:38:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] u svom prvom radnom mjestu

877
00:38:15,559 --> 00:38:16,260
[SPEAKER_00] jednu učenicu

878
00:38:16,260 --> 00:38:18,239
[SPEAKER_00] samo zato da mi se napuni satnica

879
00:38:18,239 --> 00:38:20,119
[SPEAKER_00] koja je bila najlošija,

880
00:38:20,119 --> 00:38:21,579
[SPEAKER_00] a završila je kao najbolja

881
00:38:21,579 --> 00:38:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] na kraju godine.

882
00:38:22,420 --> 00:38:22,619
[SPEAKER_00] Jel?

883
00:38:22,619 --> 00:38:24,440
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, sve se to može razviti.

884
00:38:24,440 --> 00:38:26,699
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ovo je važno što se rekao.

885
00:38:26,699 --> 00:38:27,360
[SPEAKER_01] To sam već čula

886
00:38:27,360 --> 00:38:29,659
[SPEAKER_01] od ove naše violinistice

887
00:38:29,659 --> 00:38:31,119
[SPEAKER_01] od Ivane Defar.

888
00:38:31,119 --> 00:38:32,820
[SPEAKER_01] Ona mi je to isto rekla

889
00:38:32,820 --> 00:38:34,380
[SPEAKER_01] u vrijeme kad smo obje

890
00:38:34,380 --> 00:38:35,300
[SPEAKER_01] imale manju djecu.

891
00:38:35,300 --> 00:38:36,239
[SPEAKER_01] Mi je rekla gled

892
00:38:36,239 --> 00:38:37,340
[SPEAKER_01] taj sluh

893
00:38:37,340 --> 00:38:38,420
[SPEAKER_01] to nije ta teza.

894
00:38:38,420 --> 00:38:39,320
[SPEAKER_01] Ima, nema.

895
00:38:39,320 --> 00:38:40,460
[SPEAKER_01] Da je uvijek to teško

896
00:38:40,460 --> 00:38:41,300
[SPEAKER_01] na tim prijemnijima

897
00:38:41,300 --> 00:38:42,840
[SPEAKER_01] u stvari procijeniti.

898
00:38:42,840 --> 00:38:43,880
[SPEAKER_00] I drugo što je to

899
00:38:43,880 --> 00:38:44,880
[SPEAKER_00] dva su aspekta.

900
00:38:44,880 --> 00:38:46,219
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, da li mozak

901
00:38:46,219 --> 00:38:47,039
[SPEAKER_00] sa mišićima

902
00:38:47,039 --> 00:38:48,340
[SPEAKER_00] čisto to je ono

903
00:38:48,340 --> 00:38:49,119
[SPEAKER_00] kao što bi se rekla

904
00:38:49,119 --> 00:38:50,039
[SPEAKER_00] usklađenost.

905
00:38:50,039 --> 00:38:51,039
[SPEAKER_00] To je vježba.

906
00:38:51,039 --> 00:38:51,239
[SPEAKER_00] Jel?

907
00:38:51,239 --> 00:38:51,900
[SPEAKER_00] To je vježba.

908
00:38:51,900 --> 00:38:53,679
[SPEAKER_00] Neki, imam kolegicu

909
00:38:53,679 --> 00:38:54,559
[SPEAKER_00] koja jednostavno isto

